<p>Item images are assigned the URL of the default CDN domain by default. This means that the URLs of item images contain the domain name "plentymarkets.com”. However, instead of the default CDN domain, you can also set up the domain of the client and save a custom subdomain for item images. For further information, refer to the <a href="/en/item/managing-items#4200">Saving own domain for image URLs</a> chapter.</p>
</div>
